{"tid":89162,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[新手]唔小心del咗linux之後入唔到windows","createTime":"2017-01-21T07:11:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-22T08:35:36.000Z","uid":48978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2380f2a434bc58160857ac86887737c69ad154d1","tid":89162,"uid":48978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T07:11:42.000Z","msg":"format咗裝elementary os 嘅disk partition<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">我認我on9</span></span><br />\n跟住reboot完就卡咗喺Grub rescue度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n攞隻windows usb 入完cmd打fixmbr之後都係入唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有咩方法解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00a85c4b996496ad3078fdf76145c00515148fda","tid":89162,"uid":48978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T07:12:53.000Z","msg":"補圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNQArGQUhsK9GqnyfzezDJ8VCfJ99hJ8zLTBakXw5UEtq?filename=jwBp75q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjwBp75q.jpg&h=60da6df8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8bea45dda4a7b531c53398086d1fbb1f8dc78dd8","tid":89162,"uid":48978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T07:43:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aae3b1128cdb6d19be76e69434fb0730bd834b0","tid":89162,"uid":45556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T07:46:57.000Z","msg":"mra 召喚<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw佢唔上連登喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2adbfc990eb6cbc0b9ed791f8c8736a7907ef3d","tid":89162,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T08:28:11.000Z","msg":"最簡咪裝多次 linux 係果個 partition 同裝埋 grub"},{"pid":"b9da650f9505907eb2f72768dbec41e907f73957","tid":89162,"uid":48978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T16:35:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最簡咪裝多次 linux 係果個 partition 同裝埋 grub</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係我割嚟裝linux個partition俾其他partition食咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65776ca078d21b571f9dd3640200f9e6027aaf08","tid":89162,"uid":54024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T16:39:40.000Z","msg":"搵隻ubuntu live cd boot入gui再搞返d partition重裝grub"},{"pid":"25cf76bea2fd63620bc84fd639940b28edaa6cf9","tid":89162,"uid":48978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T17:13:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵隻ubuntu live cd boot入gui再搞返d partition重裝grub</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/22/010746_3e28eeb0c437d234f7264769eb261b39.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F22%2F010746_3e28eeb0c437d234f7264769eb261b39.jpg&h=d08a5822&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用USB 入咗linux <br />\n不過我其實唔係想重裝 係直程del埋佢用返Windows boot loader<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係冇概念要點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5072f9c098e0616f114b20d0762337050e5389c","tid":89162,"uid":61946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T17:27:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>搵隻ubuntu live cd boot入gui再搞返d partition重裝grub</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/22/010746_3e28eeb0c437d234f7264769eb261b39.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F22%2F010746_3e28eeb0c437d234f7264769eb261b39.jpg&h=d08a5822&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用USB 入咗linux <br />\n不過我其實唔係想重裝 係直程del埋佢用返Windows boot loader<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係冇概念要點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你去返bios set返windows boot 做first priority咪得，然後係windows個disk management慢慢搞"},{"pid":"c166f80e579d41d4eb02f4e9b25ffbb02b865b02","tid":89162,"uid":71231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T17:32:10.000Z","msg":"你用usb boot 入去時，有沒有設定boot sequence？"},{"pid":"102c799ddd3d8fdf4df0a53fc4dad30311e48cd0","tid":89162,"uid":61946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T18:00:48.000Z","msg":"其實點解你一開機會入咗linux boot loader係因為你bios嘅first boot priority set咗係linux boot loader，所以如果你淨係想入返windows的話，可以入boot option揀返windows一般都係F12，但只係一次性，亦可以入bios set boot priority就部部機唔同快捷鍵，你要搞partition唔一定需要用usb/cd boot linux，windows都可以做到partitioning"},{"pid":"29d5e4b4be24739672a061e806e066d8bd8e887c","tid":89162,"uid":48978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T18:00:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>搵隻ubuntu live cd boot入gui再搞返d partition重裝grub</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/22/010746_3e28eeb0c437d234f7264769eb261b39.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F22%2F010746_3e28eeb0c437d234f7264769eb261b39.jpg&h=d08a5822&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用USB 入咗linux <br />\n不過我其實唔係想重裝 係直程del埋佢用返Windows boot loader<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係冇概念要點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你去返bios set返windows boot 做first priority咪得，然後係windows個disk management慢慢搞</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/22/015809_836ddfb26e29c447bbcd41731d9bb14d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F22%2F015809_836ddfb26e29c447bbcd41731d9bb14d.jpg&h=ced8249e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n頭兩隻係裝windows 嘅ssd <br />\n正常嚟講應該擺第一就入到windows (我隻linux裝喺第二隻hdd)<br />\n但係我咁set就淨係會入到Grub rescue度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb8c98943589d60341d5a86dc612fb9b3de3438c","tid":89162,"uid":48978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T18:07:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實點解你一開機會入咗linux boot loader係因為你bios嘅first boot priority set咗係linux boot loader，所以如果你淨係想入返windows的話，可以入boot option揀返windows一般都係F12，但只係一次性，亦可以入bios set boot priority就部部機唔同快捷鍵，你要搞partition唔一定需要用usb/cd boot linux，windows都可以做到partitioning</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔該晒巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我都唔知做乜 我隻Windows明明裝咗喺ssd(sata1) Linux喺Hdd(sata2) 但係我揀用ssd boot都係Grub rescue <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係正常嚟講會有個option講明係windows?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我個boot menu 係咁"},{"pid":"72f18e077552f7a2c40fc163c2f66be9c65662b4","tid":89162,"uid":48978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T18:08:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實點解你一開機會入咗linux boot loader係因為你bios嘅first boot priority set咗係linux boot loader，所以如果你淨係想入返windows的話，可以入boot option揀返windows一般都係F12，但只係一次性，亦可以入bios set boot priority就部部機唔同快捷鍵，你要搞partition唔一定需要用usb/cd boot linux，windows都可以做到partitioning</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔該晒巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我都唔知做乜 我隻Windows明明裝咗喺ssd(sata1) Linux喺Hdd(sata2) 但係我揀用ssd boot都係Grub rescue <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係正常嚟講會有個option講明係windows?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我個boot menu 係咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZZBhAa6bEmP3uMcj14VP4voeEkwNkZhwzkEuyr5p75z3?filename=qq7i6tN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqq7i6tN.jpg&h=fa2184a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"58237740dcc8ac5b43dd9bd5cff445a305d89c20","tid":89162,"uid":48978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T18:10:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實點解你一開機會入咗linux boot loader係因為你bios嘅first boot priority set咗係linux boot loader，所以如果你淨係想入返windows的話，可以入boot option揀返windows一般都係F12，但只係一次性，亦可以入bios set boot priority就部部機唔同快捷鍵，你要搞partition唔一定需要用usb/cd boot linux，windows都可以做到partitioning</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔該晒巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我都唔知做乜 我隻Windows明明裝咗喺ssd(sata1) Linux喺Hdd(sata2) 但係我揀用ssd boot都係Grub rescue <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係正常嚟講會有個option講明係windows?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我個boot menu 係咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZZBhAa6bEmP3uMcj14VP4voeEkwNkZhwzkEuyr5p75z3?filename=qq7i6tN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqq7i6tN.jpg&h=fa2184a5&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n順帶一提 sony 係usb嚟<br />\ntoshiba hdd 唔關事的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb652e623b39b7722d938b8294877873a2e95f0c","tid":89162,"uid":61946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T18:13:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/22/010746_3e28eeb0c437d234f7264769eb261b39.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F22%2F010746_3e28eeb0c437d234f7264769eb261b39.jpg&h=d08a5822&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用USB 入咗linux <br />\n不過我其實唔係想重裝 係直程del埋佢用返Windows boot loader<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係冇概念要點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你去返bios set返windows boot 做first priority咪得，然後係windows個disk management慢慢搞</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/22/015809_836ddfb26e29c447bbcd41731d9bb14d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F22%2F015809_836ddfb26e29c447bbcd41731d9bb14d.jpg&h=ced8249e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n頭兩隻係裝windows 嘅ssd <br />\n正常嚟講應該擺第一就入到windows (我隻linux裝喺第二隻hdd)<br />\n但係我咁set就淨係會入到Grub rescue度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你裝linux果時係裝係hdd到，但linux個boot loader係裝係 ssd定hdd到，同埋通常priority係跟boot loader唔係跟hard disk，見唔到有d咩boot loader？就咁F12入boot option又有無野睇？"},{"pid":"1b1a9e6c648e6dc8c016d1b60432f8d8a2dc0c78","tid":89162,"uid":61946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T18:30:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你去返bios set返windows boot 做first priority咪得，然後係windows個disk management慢慢搞</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/22/015809_836ddfb26e29c447bbcd41731d9bb14d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F22%2F015809_836ddfb26e29c447bbcd41731d9bb14d.jpg&h=ced8249e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n頭兩隻係裝windows 嘅ssd <br />\n正常嚟講應該擺第一就入到windows (我隻linux裝喺第二隻hdd)<br />\n但係我咁set就淨係會入到Grub rescue度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你裝linux果時係裝係hdd到，但linux個boot loader係裝係 ssd定hdd到，同埋通常priority係跟boot loader唔係跟hard disk，見唔到有d咩boot loader？就咁F12入boot option又有無野睇？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果你當時linux個boot loader係裝係ssd到，又無𠝹ssd嘅partition，有可能somehow replace 咗windows boot loader，如果係呢種情況，可能要試下用usb boot淨係裝返個windows boot loader係ssd到，sosad..."},{"pid":"b8a5854fabb73475d4f47a33d5fabfba3c208aa8","tid":89162,"uid":48978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T04:10:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/22/015809_836ddfb26e29c447bbcd41731d9bb14d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F22%2F015809_836ddfb26e29c447bbcd41731d9bb14d.jpg&h=ced8249e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n頭兩隻係裝windows 嘅ssd <br />\n正常嚟講應該擺第一就入到windows (我隻linux裝喺第二隻hdd)<br />\n但係我咁set就淨係會入到Grub rescue度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你裝linux果時係裝係hdd到，但linux個boot loader係裝係 ssd定hdd到，同埋通常priority係跟boot loader唔係跟hard disk，見唔到有d咩boot loader？就咁F12入boot option又有無野睇？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果你當時linux個boot loader係裝係ssd到，又無𠝹ssd嘅partition，有可能somehow replace 咗windows boot loader，如果係呢種情況，可能要試下用usb boot淨係裝返個windows boot loader係ssd到，sosad...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n明晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過有放法淨裝boot loader咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我有隻windows usb"},{"pid":"3d749b43d387a4b99bf9b690d6867b9f835e42c4","tid":89162,"uid":48978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T04:10:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你裝linux果時係裝係hdd到，但linux個boot loader係裝係 ssd定hdd到，同埋通常priority係跟boot loader唔係跟hard disk，見唔到有d咩boot loader？就咁F12入boot option又有無野睇？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果你當時linux個boot loader係裝係ssd到，又無𠝹ssd嘅partition，有可能somehow replace 咗windows boot loader，如果係呢種情況，可能要試下用usb boot淨係裝返個windows boot loader係ssd到，sosad...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n明晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過有方法淨裝boot loader咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我有隻windows usb</blockquote>"},{"pid":"b2a323f9a476dba4522a142284ce8106ca288d7b","tid":89162,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T06:34:54.000Z","msg":"樓主裝OS隻HDD係GPT定MBR？<br />\n<br />\nThe command in Windows 8/8.1/10 for fixing MBR is &quot;bootsect.exe&quot;.<br />\n<br />\nbootsect /nt60 drive_letter: /mbr<br />\n<br />\nthis fixes boot record of partition mapped to &quot;drive_letter:&quot; and the MBR of the disk where the partition is placed.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://superuser.com/questions/949219/how-to-fix-windows-10-boot-loader-from-windows\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsuperuser.com%2Fquestions%2F949219%2Fhow-to-fix-windows-10-boot-loader-from-windows&d=CDdQ6ncAsjMY%2BnUCY18RJ3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=5ee15012\" target=\"_blank\">http://superuser.com/questions/949219/how-to-fix-windows-10-boot-loader-from-windows</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nGPT可以試吓用 &quot;bcdboot.exe c:\\windows&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://superuser.com/questions/976938/how-do-i-repair-windows-10-uefi-gpt-disk-which-is-left-unbootable-after-deleting\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsuperuser.com%2Fquestions%2F976938%2Fhow-do-i-repair-windows-10-uefi-gpt-disk-which-is-left-unbootable-after-deleting&d=CDdQ6ncAsjMY%2BnUCY18RJ3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=87adf243\" target=\"_blank\">http://superuser.com/questions/976938/how-do-i-repair-windows-10-uefi-gpt-disk-which-is-left-unbootable-after-deleting</a>"},{"pid":"a705d063e9313943744124e58dbec16b98de09e7","tid":89162,"uid":29008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T06:44:27.000Z","msg":"你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f8fc7251dfdb83aab8a36abf57bc379a3102895","tid":89162,"uid":48978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T08:35:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主裝OS隻HDD係GPT定MBR？<br />\n<br />\nThe command in Windows 8/8.1/10 for fixing MBR is &quot;bootsect.exe&quot;.<br />\n<br />\nbootsect /nt60 drive_letter: /mbr<br />\n<br />\nthis fixes boot record of partition mapped to &quot;drive_letter:&quot; and the MBR of the disk where the partition is placed.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://superuser.com/questions/949219/how-to-fix-windows-10-boot-loader-from-windows\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsuperuser.com%2Fquestions%2F949219%2Fhow-to-fix-windows-10-boot-loader-from-windows&d=CDdQ6ncAsjMY%2BnUCY18RJ3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=5ee15012\" target=\"_blank\">http://superuser.com/questions/949219/how-to-fix-windows-10-boot-loader-from-windows</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nGPT可以試吓用 &quot;bcdboot.exe c:\\windows&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://superuser.com/questions/976938/how-do-i-repair-windows-10-uefi-gpt-disk-which-is-left-unbootable-after-deleting\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsuperuser.com%2Fquestions%2F976938%2Fhow-do-i-repair-windows-10-uefi-gpt-disk-which-is-left-unbootable-after-deleting&d=CDdQ6ncAsjMY%2BnUCY18RJ3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=87adf243\" target=\"_blank\">http://superuser.com/questions/976938/how-do-i-repair-windows-10-uefi-gpt-disk-which-is-left-unbootable-after-deleting</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用咗句bootsect /nt60 drive_letter: /mbr<br />\n入到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}